    <h1>Easiest Way to Track Protein Intake<br><span>After 40</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Most protein tracking apps were built for 25-year-old bodybuilders. That's exactly why most men over 40 quit using them within two weeks. Here's what actually works.</p>
    <p class="hero-meta">SnapProtein &nbsp;·&nbsp; 7 min read</p>
